Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.73,0:12:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.86,0:12:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫户川汐音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.22,0:12:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.48,0:12:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是我重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.68,0:12:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.41,0:12:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.88,0:12:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  关于户川同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.63,0:12:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是指转学的事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.47,0:12:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转学？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.65,0:13:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吗
