Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.93,0:13:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.06,0:13:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶紧去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.81,0:13:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音是我们重要的朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.19,0:13:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,望远镜由我来带回去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.77,0:13:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后来我店里拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.41,0:13:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,望远镜交给我来搬吧  别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.02,0:13:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.41,0:13:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音  求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.47,0:13:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们再谈一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.31,0:13:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想就这样和你告别
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.12,0:13:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从诺艾尔那里听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.37,0:13:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实现愿望的话  诺艾尔就会…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.92,0:13:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.13,0:14:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搬家是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.30,0:14:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是回到父亲那里住
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.86,0:14:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是为了诺艾尔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.65,0:14:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.01,0:14:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事有什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.18,0:14:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望大家一起无论何时都能充满欢笑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.44,0:14:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢大家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.98,0:14:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想再失去任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.99,0:14:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以到底要怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.42,0:14:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起来想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.02,0:14:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样  这种事不需要去想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.87,0:14:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你们没有天文台的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.00,0:14:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是被你拉进来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.33,0:14:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我消失  就能让诺艾尔留下的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.93,0:14:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就没问题了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.67,0:14:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音觉得这样就好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.81,0:14:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我回去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.32,0:15:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.55,0:15:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也对大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.96,0:15:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎么做才好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.00,0:15:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音是我重要的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.16,0:15:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么和我也是朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.72,0:15:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥太狡猾了  我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.77,0:15:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.99,0:15:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.53,0:15:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.39,0:15:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.84,0:15:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.24,0:15:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.61,0:15:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.37,0:15:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
