Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.83,0:16:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺艾尔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.20,0:16:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到大家的时候就明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.67,0:16:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为大家的愿望非常非常得纯洁美好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.18,0:16:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都欢笑着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.71,0:16:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家永远在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.65,0:16:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论何时心都相连着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.97,0:16:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是件非常非常美好的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.90,0:16:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  诺艾尔想看到欢笑着的大家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.70,0:16:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.60,0:16:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  这已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.44,0:16:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.71,0:17:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事做的话就回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.49,0:17:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.77,0:17:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在等乃乃香
