Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.68,0:17:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.26,0:17:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.16,0:17:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和汐音谈一谈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.28,0:17:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶紧回乃乃香那里去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.19,0:17:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.99,0:17:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  今天已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.56,0:17:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.27,0:17:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  你这几天都在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.66,0:17:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害我们好担心
