Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.62,0:18:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想让诺艾尔消失
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.78,0:18:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.71,0:18:40.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.32,0:18:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要再管我了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.45,0:18:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是户川也可以的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.00,0:18:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要五人不聚在一起就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.10,0:18:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只要我离开你们就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.84,0:18:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.37,0:19:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是让一直因为飞碟给大家添麻烦的我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.19,0:19:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可以交给笨蛋柚季
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.76,0:19:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么呢  笨蛋凑太
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.50,0:19:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你们别吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.77,0:19:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凑…太？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.94,0:19:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  柚季
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.12,0:19:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.64,0:19:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.90,0:19:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.92,0:19:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.22,0:19:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.17,0:19:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音都告诉你们了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.59,0:19:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要…这种事发生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.09,0:20:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.01,0:20:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺艾尔那天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.82,0:20:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在天文台的上空  听见了大家的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.57,0:20:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼唤飞碟的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.79,0:20:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼唤诺艾尔的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.77,0:20:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以诺艾尔才能和大家相见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.09,0:20:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与乃乃香初次相遇的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.18,0:20:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就明白了  呼唤我的人是乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.16,0:20:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常开心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.29,0:20:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和乃乃香一起共度时光
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.75,0:20:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教我唱好听的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.02,0:20:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香做的饭特别好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.69,0:21:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚季  小春  凑太  汐音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.71,0:21:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都非常温柔  让人暖暖的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.80,0:21:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺艾尔笑得非常非常开心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.32,0:21:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在很清楚地知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.94,0:21:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺艾尔想看到的是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.34,0:21:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香  汐音  小春  柚季还有凑太
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.77,0:21:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够一起欢笑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.54,0:21:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为诺艾尔最喜欢大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.82,0:21:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.56,0:21:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺艾尔必须要和大家分别
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------NEXT-------------------
