Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.82,0:23:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流星雨之夜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.40,0:23:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬请期待
